query
configuration.value:
SELECT TABLE_SCHEMA, TABLE_NAME, STR_TO_DATE(date_format(current_timestamp(),'%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') AS LOG_CREATED_ON
FROM information_schema.TABLES
where (TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-consumer-%'
or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-contact-record-%'
or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-contacts-%'
or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-task-%'
or TABLE_SCHEMA like 'mars-tenant-manager')
and TABLE_NAME not like 'EXTERNAL_REQ_RESPONSE'
and TABLE_NAME not like '%_TRANSACTION'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'BUSINESS_DAYS'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'BUSINESS_DAYS_HISTORY'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'AUDIT_LOG'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'DATE_FIELD'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'DISPLAY_LABEL'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'GRID'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'GRID_COLUMNS'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'GRID_COLUMN_PROPERTIES'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'SECTION'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_TEMPLATE_TYPE_MAP'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'UI_PERMISSIONS'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'FIELDS'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'PAGE'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'USER_ACTIVITY_DETAILS'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_SEARCH'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'PORTFOLIO'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'PRIVACY_NOTICE'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_QUEUE_FILTER'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_QUEUE_FILTER_SCOPE'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_QUEUE_FILTER_TASK_TYPES'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_FIELD'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_TEMPLATE'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_TEMPLATE_FIELD'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TASK_TYPE_PERMISSION'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'FIELD_VALIDATION'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'flyway_schema_history'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'HOLIDAY_HISTORY'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'CONTACT_RECORD_EDIT_HISTORY'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_A%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_B%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_C%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_D%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_E%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_F%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_G%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_H%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_I%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_J%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_K%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_LI%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_M%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_N%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_O%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_Q%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_R%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_S%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_T%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_U%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_V%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_X%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'ENUM_Z%'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'TRANSACTIONS'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'USER_SECURITY'
and TABLE_NAME not like 'BUSINESS_DAYS_HISTORY'
and concat(TABLE_SCHEMA,TABLE_NAME) not like 'mars-consumer-%CONSUMER_AUTHENTICATION'
and table_rows > 0
order by 2;

configuration.name: query
configuration.value: select count(*) AS MARS_COUNT from `${record:value('/TABLE_SCHEMA')}`.${record:value('/TABLE_NAME')} WHERE CREATED_ON IS NULL OR CREATED_ON < DATE_SUB(STR_TO_DATE(date_format(current_timestamp(),'%Y-%m-%d %H:00:00'), '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s'), INTERVAL 5 MINUTE);

configuration.name: query
configuration.value: select count(*) AS SF_COUNT from MARSDB.MARSDB_${record:value('/TABLE_NAME')} where database = '${record:value('/TABLE_SCHEMA')}' AND (created_on is null or created_on < dateadd(minute, -5, date_trunc('HOUR',convert_timezone('America/Los_Angeles', 'UTC',current_timestamp()))));
